    IsPreyingOn(ref Agent)

    Determines whether this agent is considered to be preying on the specified agent.

    Declaration
    public readonly bool IsPreyingOn(ref Agent other)
    Parameters
    Type Name Description
    Agent other

    The agent to evaluate as a potential prey. Passed by reference.
    Returns
    Type Description
    bool

    true if this agent is preying on the specified agent; otherwise, false.
    Remarks

    An agent is not considered to be preying on another agent if they are directly related or if this agent is a herbivore.

    IsThreatenedBy(ref Agent)

    Determines whether the current agent is threatened by the specified agent based on kinship, diet, and bravery.

    Declaration
    public readonly bool IsThreatenedBy(ref Agent other)
    Parameters
    Type Name Description
    Agent other

    A reference to the agent to evaluate as a potential threat.
    Returns
    Type Description
    bool

    true if the current agent is considered threatened by the specified agent; otherwise, false.
    Remarks

    An agent is not considered threatened by another agent if they are directly related, if both are herbivores, if the current agent is a carnivore or omnivore and the other is a herbivore, or if the current agent's bravery exceeds that of the other agent.
